item.description:
For those ladies who have signed up for the Better Off Bowling League session starting March 24, we will have a little get together Tuesday March 19th to meet one another and chat! Anyone is welcome to meet new folks, especially if you'd like to be an alternate for the team, but unfortunately the team is full, so this is particularly for those ladies who have already registered.

See you Tuesday!
item.name: Better Off Bowling Team Pre Game Meet and Greet
